    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Dangers of Associating With the Ungodly</strong>&mdash;The world is not to be our criterion. We are not to associate with the ungodly and partake of their spirit, for they will lead the heart away from God to the worship of false gods. The steadfast soul, firm in the faith, can do much good; he can impart blessings of the highest order to those with whom he associates, for the law of the Lord is in <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"460\"></span> his heart. But we cannot willingly associate with those who are trampling upon the law of God, and preserve our faith pure and untarnished. We shall catch the spirit, and unless we separate from them, we shall be bound up with them at last, to share their doom.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">3<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 6, 1892\" data-link=\"14057.6800001\">Manuscript 6, 1892</span>.</span></a></sup>",
