    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Beware of Those Indifferent to Religion</strong>&mdash;If children are with those whose conversation is upon unimportant, earthly things, their minds will come to the same level. If they hear the principles of religion slurred and our faith belittled, if sly objections to the truth are dropped in their hearing, these things will fasten in their minds and mold their characters.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">7<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"5T 545.1\" data-link=\"113.2668\">Testimonies for the Church 5:545</span>.</span></a></sup>",
