    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Why do our youth not consider that those who are ready to lead others into forbidden paths are easily overcome by temptation and are Satan&apos;s agents to encourage disorderly habits, to laugh at those who are conscientious and who would preserve their integrity of character?<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">14<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"YI 1-18-1894.6\" data-link=\"469.1338\">The Youth&apos;s Instructor, January 18, 1894</span>.</span></a></sup>",
