    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Live Before Strangers As You Would Before God</strong>&mdash;Young friends, do not spend an hour in the company of those who would unfit you for the pure and sacred work of God. Do nothing before strangers that you would not do before your father and mother, or that you would be ashamed of before Christ and the holy angels.",
